      "Work spans students, professionals, communities, and partner-led programs.",
    ],
    links: [{ label: "Website", href: "https://theseconddesign.com" }],
  },

  {
    id: "howtocbc",
    years: "Jul 2021 — Sep 2022",
    org: "HowToCBC.com",
    role: "Co-founder",
    badge: "PAST",
    highlights: [
      "Validated the CBC platform idea by becoming the power user first.",
      "Built deep expertise in cohort-based course creation + distribution realities.",
      "Partnered with multiple CBC platforms; learned internet outreach + marketing.",
    ],
  },
  {
